{"tid":1792314,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【集思廣益】聖誕送禮勤","createTime":"2019-12-21T14:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T15:15:45.000Z","uid":326032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"560f3dbe18d24a3dcab926a74199294e620fb91c","tid":1792314,"uid":326032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T14:05:50.000Z","msg":"聖誕節仲有4日就到，除咗還押的手足，出面嘅手足都好重要。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然已經有好幾個組織會攪聖誕大餐俾手足放鬆吓、食好d，但硬係覺得有d手足怕一鑊熟+認為要留俾更加有需要嘅人，所以唔去慶祝，收埋收埋。<br />\n<br />\n如果我係街邊送d聖誕咭+小禮物好唔好？叫做係d心意，雖然幫唔到d咩，亦都做唔到習種咁令人全身發熱，但都希望大家會開心吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係我諗唔到送咩小禮物，其實我好怕係街外食人地手製嘅嘢，好怕出事，送d朱古力/奶茶沖劑，糖好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，有密封包裝，你哋會唔會想收到？仲有咩想要？<br />\n<br />\n係喇，今年係街報佳音唱改編聖誕歌會唔會俾人啦呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：暗瘡肥婆，最後會唔會因為你的樣子如何而無人拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f127e8ae21960ccbef2e2fd04fbb3704c57f0c","tid":1792314,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T14:07:05.000Z","msg":"出席活動最好！<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n幫手推聽日行動！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wNseGbN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwNseGbN.jpg&h=ddc43c1c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QznY7RN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQznY7RN.jpg&h=471df848&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［主線任務］聽日1530嘅維吾爾族集會獲不反對通知書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1791988\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1791988</a><br />\n- 分享自